{"tid":1220442,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我係專做中老年app既人，希望大家比長輩圖我","createTime":"2019-06-14T04:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T07:13:19.000Z","uid":112342,"like":383,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"eac22471160ebbd10ea3a9075395180899b2d3e0","tid":1220442,"uid":112342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"大家好，簡單講我一直都係target 長輩既開發者，有一個長輩圖app有15k active users ,唔算好多但係一萬五入面有十分之一既人share出去都可以好多，希望大家可以比反送中長輩圖我，我收集到差唔多就會加入個app<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLfDVDh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLfDVDh.png&h=1532319c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有我開左個social network for 中老年，岩岩起步唔算多人用 得200人左右，如果有心既可以開個ac po反送中片/圖上去 email亂寫就得。希望好似做到好多人都反佔中令佢地改變想法（記得改個中老年名同icon佢地先覺得你係同類）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSfo6Mm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSfo6Mm.png&h=70eecac3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6FOFpx2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FOFpx2.png&h=608fb6ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地好多都藍絲，我預左今次會無好多users，但係都無計了可以改變一個人係一個人"},{"pid":"1876e541633b2848879b3de1fa784ae08b362417","tid":1220442,"uid":147001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"37d2b4ccf11ac5fd49090794b525d51209d5554e","tid":1220442,"uid":70423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:13:29.000Z","msg":"廢中廢老一個都不能少"},{"pid":"fb7c94a0b55370f7ccc29ec1ba9a4acbbfb0a83b","tid":1220442,"uid":4419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:13:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"88bc6b390fb8021de6badc0cb3ac5752fc48e468","tid":1220442,"uid":47546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:14:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b68a6cf78bc9a5c9105ee722d3dcd193b0ea7b2","tid":1220442,"uid":67574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:15:27.000Z","msg":"